fields.description:
When analyzing a project for iPhone, the results always return a grade of N/A.

*Steps to reproduce issue*:
1. Create a default Alloy project.
2. Run Code Analysis for iPhone on the project.
3. Notice that the results have N/A for grades under the Project Score tab.

*Expected Results*:
A grade is provided for iPhone, like the other platforms

*Notes*:
This is not a regression as it also occurs in 3.5.0.GA
fields.summary: Code Analyzer: Analyzing for iPhone always has grade of N/A
